description:
Danny chats with actress Jodi Benson, the iconic voice behind Ariel in Disney's The Little Mermaid. Jodi has a new book out September 13 called Part of My World, and she stops by Everything Iconic to talk about recording the legendary ballad, working with Howard Ashman, voicing Barbie in the Toy Story franchise, and so many more behind the scenes stories from the recording of the classic film!
